node.text: The audio at the very end 🥺🥰 The good news with this braid is that the messier and wonkier it is the better it looks 😍 it’s supposed to be irregular so you’ll start doing a Dutch braid and only add in hair every third or so cross over - does that make sense?! Easier to watch 💁🏼‍♀️ let me know if you try it!
